<p class="p1">Other features of the rail system include friction wheel carriage drive, and sewing machine swing-out for adjustment or needle looper changes. The AC variable speed drive permits stitch or stitch multiplier changes at will.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Metal-sensing proximity switches replace the old mechanical limit switches, a vast improvement over traditional rail systems.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>All of the old belts, pulleys, clutches, rack gears and carriage wheels are a thing of the past, meaning fewer wear parts in your rail assembly.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1">The Merrow Rail system is offered with a choice of selvedge clamps or pins.</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">Standard Features:<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1">Lightweight but unbreakable steel construction.</p>
<p class="p1">Push button control.</p>
<p class="p1">Rubber tire free-wheeling wheels on both stand and carriage.</p>
<p class="p1">1/3 HP motor drive for 115/60/1 with 3 wire grounded power cord.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1">Adjustable automatic stop for varying length of seam.</p>
<p class="p1">Positive gear-driven carriage with automatic electric clutch drive.</p>
<p class="p1">Adjustable selvedge pins or clamps for varying fabric widths - permits centering fabric in the machine.</p>
<p class="p1">Sewing light.</p>
<p class="p1">Optional stainless steel pin for processing wet fabrics.</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">Optional Equipment:</p>
<p class="p1">Automatic return to starting point.</p>
<p class="p1">Manually or automatically controlled stitch multiplication to double the number of stitches at the selvedges.</p>
<p class="p1">Automatic release of completed seams.</p>
<p class="p1">Automatic trimmer and waste removal system.</p>
<p class="p1">Foot operated truck locks to position machine in sewing location.</p>
