n a standard motor table.','The 70-D3B-2 HP has been tested on paint roller fabrics, air filtration fabrics, insulation and foam products.  It will be mounted on a  standard table and can be setup with a puller for more sensitive materials. ','','','','72157607121841610','500030','MERROW 8SDT','MERROW 3SDT - 8SDT ','','6-82-6','105','72','501','7.5 inches','8 inches','12.25 inch','26 lbs','Wet or Dry Environments','70 decibel','114 F Max','Compaitble with Merrow Ziggurat and other tables, rails or automated machines (see OEM Guide)','1725 RPM, 60 Hz, 1/2 HP, 110 or 220 volts, 1 or 3 phase','All fabrics, both woven and nonwoven, with the exception of extremely loose, delicate or high-pile fabrics.','14" x 15" x 16"','40 lbs','Merrow 70-D3B-2 HP Industrial Sewing Machine for Joining High Pile Fabric and Material','merrow, 70-D3B-2 HP, 70d3b2 high pile, 70d3b2 hp, 70d3b2hp, 70 Class, merrow machine, industrial sewing machines, sewing machine, industrial sewing machine, end-to-end seaming, fabric joining, textile finishing, seamer, serger, seam welder, welder, seam sealer, sewing seams,end-to-end sewing, merrowing, woven sewing, knitted sewing, non-woven sewing, butted seam, endwise seaming, overlock sewing, sewing machinery, overlock, factory sewing machines, overlocker, sew machine, overlocking machines, straight seam, square seam, sewing thick fabric, sewing thick material, overlock stitch','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 HP Industrial Sewing Machine for High Pile Fabrics sews a flat butted seam on Material up to 2" thick. The HP model was designed specifically to deliver a superior sewn edge on thick fabrics at more than 2000RPM.','','','','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/linecard_70-D3B-2_HP.pdf','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/continuousprocessing_lineup.pdf','','','','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/70d3b2hp_linecard_icon.jpg','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/continuousprocessing_lineup_icon.jpg','','','','Download a Printable Linecard for the 70-D3B-2 HP','Download the Continuous Processing Lineup Card','','','',2905),(10,28,'70','','','5','9009',76793444,'yes','70-D3B-2 LS','TWO THREAD, LOCKED STITCH BUTT SEAMING MACHINE','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS is a the worlds best <b>two thread </b>butt seaming machine for light to mid-weight material. Designed to create a locked 16MM (5/8") Stitch the 70-D3B-2 LS is the most reliable way to secure two butt-ends of material','70d3b2ls','70','','2250','101MM - 305MM (4-12 SPI)','16MM (5/8")','butt-seam','','','TWO THREAD','1','2','1','Sewing a Locked Stitch','','http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F9k6016Izj4','','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS industrial sewing machine creates a two-thread butted seam on woven and non-woven goods.  The second thread acts as a ''locked-stitch'' and is designed to lock the joining stitches in place. </p><p> The  LS model creates an effective end-end seam for operations that require added security or for fabrics that will undergo a napping process. </p><p> The <? echo $machine; ?> can be configured to produce a butted, gap, or overlap seam to achieve optimum results, according to the fabrics and manufacturing processes used.','The 70-D3B-2 LS uses two threads and a new threading system to create the 16MM (5/8") Locked Stitch. The second thread tension and thread tube are accessible and allow the sewing head to deliver the same reliable performance at 2250RPM. We have modified the base model 70-D3B-2, reducing cost and creating efficiencies for companies that own other versions of the 70-D3B-2','The traditional 16MM (5/8") Butt Seam stitch is ideal for joining fabrics, however in the case the stitch should not be removed (or cannot be compromised) the 70-D3B-2 LS should be used to Lock the Stitch (using two threads). The 70-D3B-2 LS was designed for processes that create significant and unpredictable tension on the seam. \r\n','The 70-D3B-2 LS has been designed for Napping and Shearing processes. It is also used in Billboard construction and hook and look manufacturing. The effectiveness of the locked stitch allows this 70 Class Machine to have <strong> broad appeal to markets outside of textile finishing </strong> (where the stitch is often removed) where joining materials with a PERMANENT FLAT SEAM is desirable.','','','','72157624929046399','500026','MERROW 8SDT','MERROW 3SDT - 8SDT ','','6-82-6','105','72','501','7.5 inches','8 inches','12.25 inch','26 lbs','Wet or Dry Environments','70 decibel','114 F Max','Compaitble with Merrow Ziggurat and other tables, rails or automated machines (see OEM Guide)','1725 RPM, 60 Hz, 1/2 HP, 110 or 220 volts, 1 or 3 phase','All fabrics, both woven and nonwoven, with the exception of extremely loose, delicate or high-pile fabrics.','14" x 15" x 16"','40 lbs','Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS Two Thread Industrial Sewing Machine for Sewing a Locked Stitch on Joined Fabric','merrow, 70-D3B-2 LS, 70d3b2 lock stitch, 70d3b2 ls, 70d3b2ls, 70 Class, 70-D3B-2 Two Thread, merrow machine, industrial sewing machines, sewing machine, industrial sewing machine, end-to-end seaming, fabric joining, textile finishing, seamer, serger, seam welder, welder, seam sealer, sewing seams,end-to-end sewing, merrowing, woven sewing, knitted sewing, non-woven sewing, butted seam, endwise seaming, overlock sewing, sewing machinery, overlock, factory sewing machines, overlocker, sew machine, overlocking machines, straight seam, square seam, sewing thick fabric, sewing thick material, overlock stitch, permanent flat seam, napping process, secure stitch, ','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS industrial sewing machine creates a two-thread butted seam on woven and non-woven goods. The second thread acts as a ''locked-stitch'' and is designed to lock the joining stitches in place. ','','','','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/linecard_70-D3B-2_LS.pdf','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/continuousprocessing_lineup.pdf','','','','http://marketing-downloads.s3.amazonaws.com/70d3b2ls_linecard_icon